==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Among people, in the heavens.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén jīan tīan shàng

===Phrase===
'''[[人間|人间]][[天]][[上]]''' 

# (''idiom'') Describes two people who are separated by a great distance.
# (''idiom'') Heaven on earth.

===Alternate forms===
[[人間]][[天]][[上]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

